:::{.Theorem #theoremrationals}

## The rationals are the coolest field

Let $(M,&lt;)$ be a partially ordered set, where $&lt;$ represents 'coolness of fields'. Then $\mathbb{Q}$ is a maximal element in $M$.

:::

